OL,3,CMurder accused 'upset and crying' at
OL,4,Cscene and blamed ex-partner, court told
OL,6,FThe man accused of murdering Natalie
OL,7,FMcNally, who was pregnant with his
OL,8,Funborn child, told police at the scene
OL,9,Fthat her ex-partner was responsible,
OL,10,Fhis trial has heard.
OL,12,FThe 32-year-old died after being
OL,13,Fbeaten and stabbed in her Lurgan home
OL,14,Fon December 18 2022. She was 15 weeks
OL,15,Fpregnant.
OL,17,FStephen McCullagh, 36, of Woodland
OL,18,FGardens in Lisburn, denies murder.
OL,20,FOn Tuesday morning, the trial heard
OL,21,Ffrom two police witnesses.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
