OL,3,CMurder accused 'upset and crying' at
OL,4,Cscene and blamed ex-partner, court told
OL,6,FAn officer who arrived at the scene on
OL,7,FMonday 19 December described seeing
OL,8,Fthe defendant "upset and crying" as he
OL,9,Fwas taken out of the house.
OL,11,FHe also described how upstairs Natalie
OL,12,Fwas lying on her back and he could see
OL,13,Fa puncture wound in her neck.
OL,15,FHe told the jury there was blood on
OL,16,Fthe wall and in a dog bowl near the
OL,17,Fvictim as if had been used to
OL,18,F"collect" blood.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
