FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772012402
OL,3,CMurder accused 'upset and crying' at
OL,4,Cscene and blamed ex-partner, court told
OL,6,FHe also noticed a knife on the floor.
OL,7,FThe court also heard from the on-call
OL,8,Fdetective sergeant who was responsible
OL,9,Ffor liaising between those on the
OL,10,Fground and senior officers.
OL,12,FThe court heard he was informed that
OL,13,FStephen McCullagh told police at the
OL,14,Fscene: "I know what happened. The ex
OL,15,Fpartner has done this".
OL,17,FThe detective sergeant was the one who
OL,18,Fthen directed that Mr McCullagh be
OL,19,Farrested on suspicion of murder and
OL,20,Ftaken to Banbridge police station.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
