OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772012402
OL,3,CMurder accused 'upset and crying' at
OL,4,Cscene and blamed ex-partner, court told
OL,6,FThe prosecution claim Mr McCullagh
OL,7,Fplanned a "calculated and premeditated
OL,8,Fmurder" and tried to get away with it
OL,9,Fwith a cover story and peddled a false
OL,10,Falibi.
OL,12,FThe jury were also shown pictures of
OL,13,Fthe scene and ariel photographs of
OL,14,FNatalie McNally's Silverwood Green
OL,15,Fhome.
OL,17,FThe trial is expected to last five
OL,18,Fweeks.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
